                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
                            Newspapers and magazines available
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-center p-6">
                        <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button text-4xl text-amber-600 mb-4"
                        ></i>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                            Device Charging
